<p class="govuk-body">This pattern lets the user change the language used in a service from English to Welsh and from Welsh to English.</p>

<h2 id="when-to-use" class="govuk-heading-l">When to use</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">Use the Welsh language toggle when a service is available in Welsh.</p>

